---
title: Baked Chicken & Peri Peri Sauce for Dinner with Spiced Pear Crumble for Dessert
description: If you haven’t tried our peri peri sauce then it’s time to rectify! Drizzle it over juicy chicken thigh, dunk in your favourite roast veg,
and finish is off with and fresh and crunchy slaw. You’re peri peri experience awaits!

